[alerts_://<name>]
alert_category = Select an Alert Category. For all options, clear the field by clicking on the 'X' button on the right.
alert_severity = Select Alert Severity(ies).
alert_status = Select an Alert Status. For all options, clear the field by clicking on the 'X' button on the right. (Default: false)
alert_type = Select Alert Type(s).
emc_admin_account = Select the EMC admin account.
emc_ip = Type the EMC IP address.
from_timestamp = Type the timestamp according to this format: YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SS+timeszone, e.g. - 2022-10-01T00:00:00+05:00 (Default: None)
index = (Default: default)
interval = Time interval of input in seconds.
notification_email = Email address(es) to be notified if an error occurs or is resolved. For multiple emails, use a comma (e.g. admin@admin.com,adam@example.com).
sites = Type specific Site-ID (e.g. 3). For multiple Sites, use a comma (e.g. 3,5,7). For a range of Sites, use a dash (e.g. 3-7).

